◆ Dim()

const ArrayXd & Dim ( bool  include_one_minus_x = true)

Returns the average diffusion coefficients.

\[ D_{im} = \frac{(1-x_i)}{\sum_{j\ne i}x_j/\mathscr{D}_{ij}} \]

If include_one_minus_x is false, the \(1-x_i\) term taken to be 1. This is sometimes useful when only the partial evaluation of Dim is required.
